Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cmput301.w19t06.theundesirablejackals.user.User

  • public class User
extends java.lang.Object
    This class handles the users interaction with the application including book request, owned book collection, friends, notifications, and borrowed books.
    See Also:
    BookRequestList, UserNotification, Geolocation, BookToInformationMap, UserList
